1dc64251f59b7","tid":1427523,"uid":273889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"機場係玩文宣<br />\n<br />\n夠膽勇武不如勇敢嗌英文口號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54b1ee877541ff59e52a6b13652f3e10cffab64","tid":1427523,"uid":123725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"帶個女性最愛小包包 着條短褲仔去和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申着左好多個禮拜長褲 終於可以俾佢抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b54974d118d07124012b4ad2d2883f8aa378021","tid":1427523,"uid":289300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"推，理性分析"},{"pid":"4dfff74cdc591857712df26089112a7a746655f4","tid":1427523,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9/8 終極和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"9e66503c0038e2d81586116c992d1e738c7860a9","tid":1427523,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"嗰日我會同其他巴打派乾糧同飲品<br />\n餓抵同學生 優先拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d996a44440d4b5ee778efd39427cbe5aef94fd40","tid":1427523,"uid":291689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"Push push"},{"pid":"6442cf9cfb470b33c2ba9a44287bc963b0eb3d23","tid":1427523,"uid":263344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deb3dee220fae378ed86e18a939a01243eefb92e","tid":1427523,"uid":142817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"借acc<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知好多人睇到我地航空界勇武聲明喊哂<br />\n我知好多人好期待我地行動升級<br />\n我知好多人吹奏8/9-11衝機場<br />\n<br />\n拿，機場我哋主場，你班友搵盤冰水淋頭聽我講<br />\n<br />\n機場唔同狗屋 唔同立法會<br />\n第一 你一衝入禁區就變恐襲<br />\n第二 根據相關法例 機場特警（又名速龍）可用實彈<br />\n佢地就一日到黑著住件加細碼制服陀槍四圍行嘅<br />\n我幻想狗狗失控就會開真槍<br />\n<br />\n我地唔知邊個吹奏8/9-11衝機場<br />\n本住不割席 不分化呢隻中指<br />\n<br />\n我宣布 8/9-11 係超級和理非限定<br />\n請用愛與和平向全世界解釋返林鄭同黑警嘅嘅臭史<br />\n<br />\n最後 好重要<br />\n<br />\n我地要少少時間籌備航空界聲明提及的升級行動<br />\n各位參加 8月9-11 的自發活動時請保持冷靜 <br />\n與鬼保持一個身位嘅距離<br />\n唔好玩爛我地個場<br />\n<br />\n最最後<br />\n8月9-11 唔好中計 唔好俾黑警end 我地個game<br />\n<br />\nAttach:<br />\n《航空保安規例》<br />\n(第494章第53、54及55條)<br />\n任何人&nbsp;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)以通過為進出禁區而設計的閘門或孔口以外的方法進入或離開禁區，或企圖以通過該等閘門或孔口以外的方法進入或離開禁區；<br />\n(b)攀爬或企圖攀爬任何構成沿着禁區周邊的欄障一部分的牆壁或柵欄或其他東西；<br />\n(c)移走、移動或更改或企圖移走、移動或更改任何構成沿着禁區周邊的欄障一部分的牆壁或柵欄或其他東西；<br />\n(d)干擾放置在禁區周邊或禁區內用以偵測任何企圖未獲授權而進入禁區的人的保安器件，<br />\n即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第5級罰款及監禁2年。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8f0978874482d1994851df8b581123329567fa2","tid":1427523,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n留返俾機場巴絲升級<br />\n唔好好似上次地鐵咁騎劫"},{"pid":"f31b8c5ed0f0712e4d62adb73c06d15e103b87b9","tid":1427523,"uid":17503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"和你飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcfb9f06f5e7a13b3475e5a96c9fc9a823ad95f","tid":1427523,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ff7500bf742624cf6cb06ae276d14b3ba83df70","tid":1427523,"uid":277145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964d5a037370e3bd70d97cfd146140b07115b0ad","tid":1427523,"uid":291545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:23:47.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"042a1c02cd46513b388a3658d9b46befc11ed74c","tid":1427523,"uid":279937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:26:31.000Z